Deltona.WOTF-TV: WOTF-TV, virtual channel 26 (UHF digital channel 49), is a UniMás-affiliated television station serving Orlando, Florida, United States that is licensed to Daytona Beach. The station is owned by Entravision Communications, which also operates Melbourne-licensed Univision-owned station WVEN-TV (channel 43) through a local marketing agreement with the Univision Local Media subsidiary of Univision Communications. The two stations share studios located in Altamonte Springs; WOTF's transmitter is located near Orange City, Florida.
